<b><A HREF="/heritage">The Heritage Foundation</a></b>
</center><p>
<h3>Appendix</h3>
<CENTER><H2>SUPPORTING DOCUMENTATION </H2>


<B><CITE>By Brett Schaefer</CITE></B>
</P></CENTER>
<P>

<P><B>1.</B> <a href="#1">Major Overseas Commitments of the United States</a>
</P>
<P><B>2.</B> <a href="app2_1.gif">United States Military Personnel Overseas</a>
</P>
<P><B>3.</B> Proliferation of Weapons of Mass Destruction and Their  Delivery
Systems
<ul>
<LI><a href="map_1.gif">Map 1</a>: Nuclear, Biological, Chemical Proliferation
<li><a href="map_2.gif">Map 2</a>: Ballistic Missile Proliferation
</ul>
