<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<TITLE>DAVID MASON -- Heritage </TITLE>
<H3>
DAVID MASON</H3>
<HR>
<B>SENIOR FELLOW, CONGRESSIONAL STUDIES</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/mason.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
Mason studies the problems that critics say have left Congress unresponsive to the taxpayers and beholden to special interests.  Under his direction, Heritage published <i>The Ruling Class: Inside the Imperial Congress</i> (1993), an assessment of pervasive institutional problems and solutions. He also directed Heritage's liaison program with the executive branch, and identified and recommended conservative candidates for key public policy positions. A former Deputy Assistant Secretary of Defense  and  eight-year  veteran  of  Capitol  Hill,  Mason  previously served as Staff Director to then-House Minority Whip Rep. Trent Lott, R-Miss.

