Content-type: text/html
</DOCHDR>

<html>
<head>
<TITLE>The Heritage Foundation Commentary 1995 Archive -- Heritage </TITLE>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<blockquote>
